  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rise From Nothing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin your journey as a poor peasant in a medieval world. With only a small mine to your name, extract ore, sell resources, and reinvest your earnings to survive and grow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/1185312d68b588195730fef77f69c55d.poster.avif?t=1773772787\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/1185312d68b588195730fef77f69c55d.webm?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/1185312d68b588195730fef77f69c55d.mp4?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Multiple Sources of Income</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand beyond mining by investing in farming, livestock, and woodcutting. Harvest crops, gather animal products, cut trees, and turn raw materials into steady profit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/bc2ef4bf37176a84f56889525deed583.poster.avif?t=1773772787\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/bc2ef4bf37176a84f56889525deed583.webm?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/bc2ef4bf37176a84f56889525deed583.mp4?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/10f017262ef9e25c409aa9d7a39307e4.poster.avif?t=1773772787\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/10f017262ef9e25c409aa9d7a39307e4.webm?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/10f017262ef9e25c409aa9d7a39307e4.mp4?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/8ff73304aac9ec2241233498257f4158.poster.avif?t=1773772787\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/8ff73304aac9ec2241233498257f4158.webm?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/8ff73304aac9ec2241233498257f4158.mp4?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Automate and Expand</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tired of doing everything yourself? Hire workers to run your operations and keep production going. As your income grows, purchase land, construct houses, and rent them out for passive income.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/4c60984c3e937fc37f4d251d7b40ac5e.poster.avif?t=1773772787\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/4c60984c3e937fc37f4d251d7b40ac5e.webm?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/4c60984c3e937fc37f4d251d7b40ac5e.mp4?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take Risks and Gamble</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your luck through card games or place bets on brutal fights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/91e06c6a069c7f7b2b25aae4cb280db6.poster.avif?t=1773772787\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/91e06c6a069c7f7b2b25aae4cb280db6.webm?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278710/extras/91e06c6a069c7f7b2b25aae4cb280db6.mp4?t=1773772787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
