      "review_text": "Early access means there's room to improve so I'll give honest feedback. The game has very good promise. I can even overlook the very basic and clunky UI. But the tutorial is horrible. Even me, someone who wanted to learn the game and play therefore opened the menu like 6 times in 10minutes, it does a horrible job of teaching me what to do when I start the game. I couldn't find food, couldn't buy it from the shops? I know it's probably my bad I failed with the controls or something BUT you have a 9 page tutorial. It should've been easy for me to learn how to eat and what to eat fast while dying from hunger. I hope you guys get a chance to actually work on this game and make it more accessible, but as it stands, cannot recommend.",
      "timestamp_created": 1773831008
    },
    {
      "review_id": "220973863",
      "author_steamid": "76561198150275344",
      "voted_up": false,
      "votes_up": 1,
      "playtime_at_review": 84,
      "review_text": "1 of the worst in early development games ive ever come across its as if the developer only invested £50 into the game its very bare bones the ui is horrid i have a high end gaming pc with a 5070ti and i cant see the health bars or food/drink bars so ill randomly die and theres nothing u can do about that because theres no graphics change option and the ui scale goes off my screen so i can select items to buy. basically its a dumpster fire of a game. even at £3.99 its still a waste of money.\n\nupdate the games had some updates since my review. theyve sorted the off ballance ui where the on screen ui would not be viewable. theres an issue with the food and drink draining way to fast be nice if you the game maker could change it or give us an option to change the food and drink drain speed. also even if your food and drink bars are full and you sleep at 6pm you wake up hungry and dying what the hell is he sleep walking toi the gym or something lol. with those bugs still the games unplayable and not fun running back and forward to the well and tavern to get water and food.",
      "timestamp_created": 1773835914
